For Linux/Mac
--------------
To run simulations in matlab with SCOTS you need compile the mexfile

1. set up the mex compiler in Matlab:

  >> mex -setup C++

2. edit the make file and adjust the variables

  a) MATLABROOT
  b) CUDDPATH

3. in a terminal run

  $ make



For Windows
--------------
1. unpack the compressed file (cuddwin64/lib/CUDD.7z) the CUDD.lib file be in 
the directory (cuddwin64/lib).

2. From inside MATLAB while you are in this (mexfiles) directory:

  >> mex -setup C++
  >> makewin